var book = {
	"name": "1 John",
	"numChapters": 5,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>That which was from the beginning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30542A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30542A\"></sup> which we have heard, which we have seen with our eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30542B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30542B\"></sup> which we have looked at and our hands have touched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30542C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30542C\"></sup>—this we proclaim concerning the Word of life.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The life appeared;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30543D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30543D\"></sup> we have seen it and testify to it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30543E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30543E\"></sup> and we proclaim to you the eternal life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30543F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30543F\"></sup> which was with the Father and has appeared to us.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>We proclaim to you what we have seen and heard,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30544G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30544G\"></sup> so that you also may have fellowship with us. And our fellowship is with the Father and with his Son, Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30544H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30544H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>We write this<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30545I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30545I\"></sup> to make our joy complete.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30545J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30545J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>This is the message we have heard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30546K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30546K\"></sup> from him and declare to you: God is light;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30546L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30546L\"></sup> in him there is no darkness at all.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If we claim to have fellowship with him and yet walk in the darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30547M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30547M\"></sup> we lie and do not live out the truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30547N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30547N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But if we walk in the light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30548O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30548O\"></sup> as he is in the light, we have fellowship with one another, and the blood of Jesus, his Son, purifies us from all sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30548P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30548P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If we claim to be without sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30549Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30549Q\"></sup> we deceive ourselves and the truth is not in us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30549R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30549R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If we confess our sins, he is faithful and just and will forgive us our sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30550S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30550S\"></sup> and purify us from all unrighteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30550T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30550T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If we claim we have not sinned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30551U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30551U\"></sup> we make him out to be a liar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30551V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30551V\"></sup> and his word is not in us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30551W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30551W\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>My dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30552A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30552A\"></sup> I write this to you so that you will not sin. But if anybody does sin, we have an advocate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30552B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30552B\"></sup> with the Father—Jesus Christ, the Righteous One.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He is the atoning sacrifice for our sins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30553C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30553C\"></sup> and not only for ours but also for the sins of the whole world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30553D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30553D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>We know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30554E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30554E\"></sup> that we have come to know him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30554F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30554F\"></sup> if we keep his commands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30554G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30554G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Whoever says, “I know him,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30555H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30555H\"></sup> but does not do what he commands is a liar, and the truth is not in that person.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30555I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30555I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But if anyone obeys his word,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30556J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30556J\"></sup> love for God is truly made complete in them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30556K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30556K\"></sup> This is how we know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30556L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30556L\"></sup> we are in him:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Whoever claims to live in him must live as Jesus did.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30557M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30557M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Dear friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30558N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30558N\"></sup> I am not writing you a new command but an old one, which you have had since the beginning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30558O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30558O\"></sup> This old command is the message you have heard.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Yet I am writing you a new command;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30559P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30559P\"></sup> its truth is seen in him and in you, because the darkness is passing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30559Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30559Q\"></sup> and the true light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30559R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30559R\"></sup> is already shining.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30559S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30559S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Anyone who claims to be in the light but hates a brother or sister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30560T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30560T\"></sup> is still in the darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30560U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30560U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Anyone who loves their brother and sister lives in the light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30561V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30561V\"></sup> and there is nothing in them to make them stumble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30561W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30561W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But anyone who hates a brother or sister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30562X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30562X\"></sup> is in the darkness and walks around in the darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30562Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30562Y\"></sup> They do not know where they are going, because the darkness has blinded them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30562Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30562Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I am writing to you, dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30563AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30563AA\"></sup>because your sins have been forgiven on account of his name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30563AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30563AB\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I am writing to you, fathers,because you know him who is from the beginning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30564AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30564AC\"></sup>I am writing to you, young men,because you have overcome<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30564AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30564AD\"></sup> the evil one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30564AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30564AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I write to you, dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30565AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30565AF\"></sup>because you know the Father.I write to you, fathers,because you know him who is from the beginning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30565AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30565AG\"></sup>I write to you, young men,because you are strong,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30565AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30565AH\"></sup>and the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30565AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30565AI\"></sup> lives in you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30565AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30565AJ\"></sup>and you have overcome the evil one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30565AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30565AK\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do not love the world or anything in the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30566AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30566AL\"></sup> If anyone loves the world, love for the Father is not in them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30566AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30566AM\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For everything in the world—the lust of the flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30567AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30567AN\"></sup> the lust of the eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30567AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30567AO\"></sup> and the pride of life—comes not from the Father but from the world.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The world and its desires pass away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30568AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30568AP\"></sup> but whoever does the will of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30568AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30568AQ\"></sup> lives forever.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Dear children, this is the last hour;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30569AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30569AR\"></sup> and as you have heard that the antichrist is coming,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30569AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30569AS\"></sup> even now many antichrists have come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30569AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30569AT\"></sup> This is how we know it is the last hour.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They went out from us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30570AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30570AU\"></sup> but they did not really belong to us. For if they had belonged to us, they would have remained with us; but their going showed that none of them belonged to us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30570AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30570AV\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But you have an anointing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30571AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30571AW\"></sup> from the Holy One,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30571AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30571AX\"></sup> and all of you know the truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30571AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30571AY\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I do not write to you because you do not know the truth, but because you do know it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30572AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30572AZ\"></sup> and because no lie comes from the truth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Who is the liar? It is whoever denies that Jesus is the Christ. Such a person is the antichrist—denying the Father and the Son.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30573BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30573BA\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>No one who denies the Son has the Father; whoever acknowledges the Son has the Father also.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30574BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30574BB\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>As for you, see that what you have heard from the beginning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30575BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30575BC\"></sup> remains in you. If it does, you also will remain in the Son and in the Father.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30575BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30575BD\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And this is what he promised us—eternal life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30576BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30576BE\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I am writing these things to you about those who are trying to lead you astray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30577BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30577BF\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>As for you, the anointing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30578BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30578BG\"></sup> you received from him remains in you, and you do not need anyone to teach you. But as his anointing teaches you about all things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30578BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30578BH\"></sup> and as that anointing is real, not counterfeit—just as it has taught you, remain in him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30578BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30578BI\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And now, dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30579BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30579BJ\"></sup> continue in him, so that when he appears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30579BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30579BK\"></sup> we may be confident<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30579BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30579BL\"></sup> and unashamed before him at his coming.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30579BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30579BM\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>If you know that he is righteous,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30580BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30580BN\"></sup> you know that everyone who does what is right has been born of him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30580BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30580BO\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>See what great love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30581A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30581A\"></sup> the Father has lavished on us, that we should be called children of God!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30581B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30581B\"></sup> And that is what we are! The reason the world does not know us is that it did not know him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30581C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30581C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Dear friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30582D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30582D\"></sup> now we are children of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30582E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30582E\"></sup> and what we will be has not yet been made known. But we know that when Christ appears,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30582F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30582F\"></sup> we shall be like him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30582G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30582G\"></sup> for we shall see him as he is.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30582H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30582H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>All who have this hope in him purify themselves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30583I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30583I\"></sup> just as he is pure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30583J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30583J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Everyone who sins breaks the law; in fact, sin is lawlessness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30584K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30584K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But you know that he appeared so that he might take away our sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30585L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30585L\"></sup> And in him is no sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30585M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30585M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>No one who lives in him keeps on sinning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30586N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30586N\"></sup> No one who continues to sin has either seen him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30586O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30586O\"></sup> or known him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30586P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30586P\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30587Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30587Q\"></sup> do not let anyone lead you astray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30587R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30587R\"></sup> The one who does what is right is righteous, just as he is righteous.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30587S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30587S\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The one who does what is sinful is of the devil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30588T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30588T\"></sup> because the devil has been sinning from the beginning. The reason the Son of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30588U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30588U\"></sup> appeared was to destroy the devil’s work.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30588V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30588V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>No one who is born of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30589W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30589W\"></sup> will continue to sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30589X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30589X\"></sup> because God’s seed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30589Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30589Y\"></sup> remains in them; they cannot go on sinning, because they have been born of God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This is how we know who the children of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30590Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30590Z\"></sup> are and who the children of the devil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30590AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30590AA\"></sup> are: Anyone who does not do what is right is not God’s child, nor is anyone who does not love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30590AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30590AB\"></sup> their brother and sister.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30590AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30590AC\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For this is the message you heard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30591AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30591AD\"></sup> from the beginning:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30591AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30591AE\"></sup> We should love one another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30591AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30591AF\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Do not be like Cain, who belonged to the evil one<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30592AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30592AG\"></sup> and murdered his brother.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30592AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30592AH\"></sup> And why did he murder him? Because his own actions were evil and his brother’s were righteous.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30592AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30592AI\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not be surprised, my brothers and sisters, if the world hates you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30593AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30593AJ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>We know that we have passed from death to life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30594AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30594AK\"></sup> because we love each other. Anyone who does not love remains in death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30594AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30594AL\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Anyone who hates a brother or sister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30595AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30595AM\"></sup> is a murderer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30595AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30595AN\"></sup> and you know that no murderer has eternal life residing in him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30595AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30595AO\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This is how we know what love is: Jesus Christ laid down his life for us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30596AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30596AP\"></sup> And we ought to lay down our lives for our brothers and sisters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30596AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30596AQ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If anyone has material possessions and sees a brother or sister in need but has no pity on them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30597AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30597AR\"></sup> how can the love of God be in that person?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30597AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30597AS\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30598AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30598AT\"></sup> let us not love with words or speech but with actions and in truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30598AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30598AU\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This is how we know that we belong to the truth and how we set our hearts at rest in his presence:",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>If our hearts condemn us, we know that God is greater than our hearts, and he knows everything.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Dear friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30601AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30601AV\"></sup> if our hearts do not condemn us, we have confidence before God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30601AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30601AW\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and receive from him anything we ask,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30602AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30602AX\"></sup> because we keep his commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30602AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30602AY\"></sup> and do what pleases him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30602AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30602AZ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And this is his command: to believe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30603BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30603BA\"></sup> in the name of his Son, Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30603BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30603BB\"></sup> and to love one another as he commanded us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30603BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30603BC\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The one who keeps God’s commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30604BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30604BD\"></sup> lives in him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30604BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30604BE\"></sup> and he in them. And this is how we know that he lives in us: We know it by the Spirit he gave us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30604BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30604BF\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Dear friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30605A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30605A\"></sup> do not believe every spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30605B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30605B\"></sup> but test the spirits to see whether they are from God, because many false prophets have gone out into the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30605C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30605C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is how you can recognize the Spirit of God: Every spirit that acknowledges that Jesus Christ has come in the flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30606D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30606D\"></sup> is from God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30606E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30606E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>but every spirit that does not acknowledge Jesus is not from God. This is the spirit of the antichrist,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30607F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30607F\"></sup> which you have heard is coming and even now is already in the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30607G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30607G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You, dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30608H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30608H\"></sup> are from God and have overcome them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30608I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30608I\"></sup> because the one who is in you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30608J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30608J\"></sup> is greater than the one who is in the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30608K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30608K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They are from the world<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30609L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30609L\"></sup> and therefore speak from the viewpoint of the world, and the world listens to them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We are from God, and whoever knows God listens to us; but whoever is not from God does not listen to us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30610M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30610M\"></sup> This is how we recognize the Spirit of truth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30610N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30610N\"></sup> and the spirit of falsehood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30610O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30610O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Dear friends, let us love one another,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30611P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30611P\"></sup> for love comes from God. Everyone who loves has been born of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30611Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30611Q\"></sup> and knows God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30611R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30611R\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whoever does not love does not know God, because God is love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30612S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30612S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This is how God showed his love among us: He sent his one and only Son<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30613T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30613T\"></sup> into the world that we might live through him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30613U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30613U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This is love: not that we loved God, but that he loved us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30614V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30614V\"></sup> and sent his Son as an atoning sacrifice for our sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30614W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30614W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Dear friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30615X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30615X\"></sup> since God so loved us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30615Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30615Y\"></sup> we also ought to love one another.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30615Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30615Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>No one has ever seen God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30616AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30616AA\"></sup> but if we love one another, God lives in us and his love is made complete in us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30616AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30616AB\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is how we know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30617AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30617AC\"></sup> that we live in him and he in us: He has given us of his Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30617AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30617AD\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And we have seen and testify<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30618AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30618AE\"></sup> that the Father has sent his Son to be the Savior of the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30618AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30618AF\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If anyone acknowledges that Jesus is the Son of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30619AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30619AG\"></sup> God lives in them and they in God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30619AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30619AH\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And so we know and rely on the love God has for us.God is love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30620AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30620AI\"></sup> Whoever lives in love lives in God, and God in them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30620AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30620AJ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>This is how love is made complete<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30621AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30621AK\"></sup> among us so that we will have confidence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30621AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30621AL\"></sup> on the day of judgment:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30621AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30621AM\"></sup> In this world we are like Jesus.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There is no fear in love. But perfect love drives out fear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30622AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30622AN\"></sup> because fear has to do with punishment. The one who fears is not made perfect in love.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>We love because he first loved us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30623AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30623AO\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Whoever claims to love God yet hates a brother or sister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30624AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30624AP\"></sup> is a liar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30624AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30624AQ\"></sup> For whoever does not love their brother and sister, whom they have seen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30624AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30624AR\"></sup> cannot love God, whom they have not seen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30624AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30624AS\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And he has given us this command:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30625AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30625AT\"></sup> Anyone who loves God must also love their brother and sister.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30625AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30625AU\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Everyone who believes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30626A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30626A\"></sup> that Jesus is the Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30626B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30626B\"></sup> is born of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30626C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30626C\"></sup> and everyone who loves the father loves his child as well.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30626D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30626D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is how we know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30627E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30627E\"></sup> that we love the children of God:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30627F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30627F\"></sup> by loving God and carrying out his commands.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In fact, this is love for God: to keep his commands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30628G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30628G\"></sup> And his commands are not burdensome,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30628H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30628H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>for everyone born of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30629I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30629I\"></sup> overcomes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30629J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30629J\"></sup> the world. This is the victory that has overcome the world, even our faith.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Who is it that overcomes the world? Only the one who believes that Jesus is the Son of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30630K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30630K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is the one who came by water and blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30631L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30631L\"></sup>—Jesus Christ. He did not come by water only, but by water and blood. And it is the Spirit who testifies, because the Spirit is the truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30631M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30631M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For there are three<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30632N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30632N\"></sup> that testify:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>the Spirit, the water and the blood; and the three are in agreement.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>We accept human testimony,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30634O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30634O\"></sup> but God’s testimony is greater because it is the testimony of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30634P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30634P\"></sup> which he has given about his Son.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whoever believes in the Son of God accepts this testimony.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30635Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30635Q\"></sup> Whoever does not believe God has made him out to be a liar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30635R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30635R\"></sup> because they have not believed the testimony God has given about his Son.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And this is the testimony: God has given us eternal life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30636S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30636S\"></sup> and this life is in his Son.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30636T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30636T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Whoever has the Son has life; whoever does not have the Son of God does not have life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30637U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30637U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I write these things to you who believe in the name of the Son of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30638V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30638V\"></sup> so that you may know that you have eternal life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30638W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30638W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is the confidence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30639X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30639X\"></sup> we have in approaching God: that if we ask anything according to his will, he hears us.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30639Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30639Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And if we know that he hears us—whatever we ask—we know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30640Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30640Z\"></sup> that we have what we asked of him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30640AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30640AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If you see any brother or sister commit a sin that does not lead to death, you should pray and God will give them life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30641AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30641AB\"></sup> I refer to those whose sin does not lead to death. There is a sin that leads to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30641AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30641AC\"></sup> I am not saying that you should pray about that.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30641AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30641AD\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>All wrongdoing is sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30642AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30642AE\"></sup> and there is sin that does not lead to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30642AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30642AF\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>We know that anyone born of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30643AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30643AG\"></sup> does not continue to sin; the One who was born of God keeps them safe, and the evil one<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30643AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30643AH\"></sup> cannot harm them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30643AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30643AI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>We know that we are children of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30644AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30644AJ\"></sup> and that the whole world is under the control of the evil one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30644AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30644AK\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>We know also that the Son of God has come<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30645AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30645AL\"></sup> and has given us understanding,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30645AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30645AM\"></sup> so that we may know him who is true.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30645AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30645AN\"></sup> And we are in him who is true by being in his Son Jesus Christ. He is the true God and eternal life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30645AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30645AO\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30646AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30646AP\"></sup> keep yourselves from idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30646AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30646AQ\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;